{"text_id":245298,"tokens":["In"," this"," study",","," we"," explore"," the"," problem"," of"," personal","izing"," image"," search"," results"," on"," Flickr","."," As"," a"," popular"," image"," hosting"," and"," sharing"," platform",","," Flickr"," offers"," an"," extensive"," collection"," of"," images"," available"," for"," online"," search","."," However",","," the"," traditional"," approach"," to"," image"," search"," provides"," a"," one","-","size","-","fits","-","all"," solution"," that"," does"," not"," account"," for"," individual"," user"," preferences"," and"," interests","."," Therefore",","," the"," goal"," of"," our"," research"," is"," to"," design"," and"," implement"," a"," personalized"," image"," search"," approach"," that"," considers"," the"," context"," of"," the"," user"," to"," provide"," relevant",","," personalized"," image"," recommendations","."," ","\n\n","We"," propose"," a"," machine"," learning","-","based"," approach"," that"," lever","ages"," the"," user","'","s"," past"," behavior",","," including"," their"," search"," history"," and"," interaction"," with"," previous"," search"," results",","," to"," create"," a"," personalized"," image"," search"," engine","."," Specifically",","," we"," use"," collaborative"," filtering"," techniques"," to"," model"," the"," user","'","s"," search"," behavior"," and"," preferences"," and"," provide"," image"," recommendations"," accordingly","."," Our"," model"," also"," takes"," into"," account"," the"," relevance"," and"," diversity"," of"," the"," recommended"," images"," to"," ensure"," a"," well","-","rounded"," search"," experience"," for"," the"," user",".","\n\n","We"," evaluate"," the"," effectiveness"," of"," our"," proposed"," approach"," through"," a"," comprehensive"," set"," of"," experiments"," using"," a"," real","-","world"," dataset"," from"," Flickr","."," Our"," results"," show"," that"," our"," personalized"," image"," search"," approach"," out","performs"," the"," traditional"," approach",","," providing"," more"," relevant"," and"," diverse"," image"," recommendations"," to"," the"," user",".","  ","\n\n","Overall",","," our"," work"," attempts"," to"," solve"," the"," problem"," of"," personalized"," and"," context","-","aware"," image"," search"," by"," leveraging"," machine"," learning"," techniques"," to"," model"," the"," user","'","s"," preferences"," and"," behavior","."," Our"," approach"," has"," the"," potential"," to"," improve"," the"," user"," experience"," of"," image"," search"," platforms"," like"," Flickr"," by"," providing"," tailored"," recommendations"," that"," match"," the"," user","'","s"," interests"," and"," preferences","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}